    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>What information we collect</h2>
      <ul class="legal-page__list">
        <li>
          <strong>Booking enquiry:</strong> name, email, phone number, stay dates, room preferences, guest counts, and optional notes you type in our form.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Contact form:</strong> first and last name, email, message, and any information you voluntarily include.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Usage data (technical):</strong> when you load pages, standard server and analytics tools may process IP address and device/browser data in aggregated or logged form depending on hosting and measurement tools configured.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>How we use your information</h2>
      <ul class="legal-page__list">
        <li>To respond to booking requests and contact messages.</li>
        <li>To send booking-related emails (for example acknowledgement to you and notification to staff).</li>
        <li>To improve the website and measure basic engagement where measurement tools are enabled.</li>
        <li>To meet legal or safety obligations where required.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Payments on this website</h2>
      <p>
        Our online booking enquiry form does not collect debit or credit card numbers. If advance payment or deposit is needed, staff will explain
        secure options separately (such as transfer or payment link), according to procedures in place when you confirm.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Service providers (“processors”)</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on how you interact with us, information may pass through reputable providers that support email delivery,
        secure form relay, hosting, or measurement. Categories include email delivery infrastructure, Cloudflare Workers (when used for booking submissions),
        <strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> (when we enable it on the booking form for automated abuse reduction),
        form delivery services associated with enquiries, GitHub-hosted static site delivery, and Google measurement/tagging where activated.
      </p>
      <p>
        Those providers operate under their own terms and privacy policies. We instruct them only to assist with delivering this site or handling enquiries
        tied to reservations and contact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Cookies and similar technologies</h2>
      <p>
        We may use cookies or similar technologies for measurement or advertising performance where Google tagging is enabled on this site.
        You can restrict cookies in your browser settings. Choices offered by advertising partners may vary by region.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Booking and enquiry details are retained only as long as needed to complete your stay, handle accounting or disputes,
        comply with law, or run the business—including reasonable archival where appropriate—and then deleted or anonymised in line with our practices.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Your choices and rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may contact us to request access, correction, or deletion of personal information we hold, subject to lawful exceptions (for example
        records we must retain). If you apply from a jurisdiction with specific privacy statutes, we respond in accordance with applicable law once we verify your request.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Transfers</h2>
      <p>
        Some processors may store or process data outside India (for example United States–based clouds). Where required, safeguards such as contractual terms
        or provider certifications may apply. By submitting a form when that processing is enabled, you understand information may transit those systems solely to fulfil your enquiry.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>
        This site is aimed at travellers making lodging arrangements. Do not submit information about children unless you are their parent/guardian
        coordinating a lawful stay.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-page__block">
      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may revise this Privacy Policy periodically. Updates will appear on this page with a revised effective date where material changes occur.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="legal-page__footnote">
